So the prep is finally end here..🥹 
Got 2nd place in Men’s Physique category. So yes, koi bhi ye soch ke nhi aata ki wo 2nd hoga everybody wants to be first but jab aap kisi chiz ko bilkul shiddat se karo to oosme apne aap ko puri tarah se laga dena, oos kaam me apna 100% dena wahi decide karta hai aapka result kaisa hoga. So yaa maine to apne taraf se puri mehnat kari thi apna 100% diya tha pr lagta hai shayad meri hardwork me kuchh kami thi but it’s ok will come back stronger next year..🇮🇳 

Thank you so much guys for your appreciation 😇
